{{ttmOpenAiSimpleV1}}:
This function works with OpenAI text models without reasoning chains.

Before use, you must fill in your API key in the code for this function in the table ttm__custom_functions.

system ‚Äî string, system prompt.

user ‚Äî string, user data for processing.

model ‚Äî string, 4th series model, without reasoning chain gpt-4o, gpt-4o-mini and other similar ones without reasoning chains.

maxtokens ‚Äî number (default 4090), maximum number of tokens in the response (current maximum in OpenAI documentation).

struct ‚Äî multiline text, JSON structure for model return (structure is generated using OpenAI platform playground). If this parameter is specified, the value returned by the model will be automatically converted from a JSON string to a totum data structure.

testmode ‚Äî true/false (if not specified, then false), enables test mode and will return the full OpenAI server response along with HTTP headers as plain text.
